<description>
<p>
Bootqt is a lightweight image writer that allows you to quickly create bootable USB drives. It can also download and apply the latest versions of various Linux distributions automatically, as well as install Ventoy onto your USB, which allows you to include many ISO files within a single drive.
</p>
</description>

